export const styles = {
    container: {
        maxWidth: '800px',
        margin: '0 auto',
        padding: '20px',
        backgroundColor: '#f0f0f0',
        border: '1px solid #ccc',
        borderRadius: '8px',
        boxShadow: '0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)',
    },
    formContainer: {
        marginBottom: '20px',
        padding: '10px',
        backgroundColor: '#fff',
        border: '1px solid #e0e0e0',
        borderRadius: '4px',
        boxShadow: '0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)',
    },
    timeSlotItem: {
        marginBottom: '10px',
        padding: '10px',
        backgroundColor: '#fff',
        border: '1px solid #e0e0e0',
        borderRadius: '4px',
        boxShadow: '0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)',
        display: 'flex',
        justifyContent: 'space-between',
        alignItems: 'center',
    },
    deleteButton: {
        backgroundColor: '#ff5050',
        color: '#fff',
        border: 'none',
        padding: '5px 10px',
        borderRadius: '4px',
        cursor: 'pointer',
    },
};
